coverflowmp (1.5.0) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Add application icon and desktop integration
  * Added time delay functionality
  * Advanced features
  * Fast modus added
  * Newest features like extra keys, dynamic cover extraction while
    browser is showing already etc
  * Build changes
  * More build changes
  * Skip file auto import
  * Power saving inhibitor to prevent disruption
  * Showing clock in Pause Mode, progress and video time in browser
  * Subtract skip ranges in browser
  * Changed RESET function to optionally restrict to current folder
  * Bugfix for total videos times in Browser
  * Fall back to libmpv for browser durations when ffprobe is unavailable
  * Add ffmpeg and ffmpegthumbnailer as runtime dependencies
  * Bugfix for missing package from ffmpeg

